9 package org.locationtech.geomesa.utils.cache
10 
11 import com.clearspring.analytics.hash.MurmurHash
12 import com.typesafe.scalalogging.LazyLogging
13 
14 /**
15   * Cache key for comparing byte arrays
16   *
17   * @param bytes bytes
18   */
19 class ByteArrayCacheKey(val bytes: Array[Byte]) extends LazyLogging {
20 
21   override def hashCode(): Int = MurmurHash.hash(bytes)
22 
23   override def equals(obj: Any): Boolean = {
24     obj match {
25       case b: ByteArrayCacheKey => java.util.Arrays.equals(bytes, b.bytes)
26       case _ => false
27     }
28   }
29 
30   // writes out the bytes as hex
31   override def toString: String =
32     bytes.map(b => f"${(b & 0xff) >>> 4}%01x${b & 0x0f}%01x").mkString("ByteArrayCacheKey[", ":", "]")
33 }
